80元<br />\nwhite object 45,305元 至 84,250元<br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理11,866元至14,064元<br />\n一級病人服務助理21,389元至25,199元<br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN 20,610 至 43,783<br />\nRN 32,675 至 52,578<br />\n<br />\n2.仇恨<br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.無保障<br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=3e1998b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n對應解決方法<br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工"},{"pid":"e101c1b345f1f4c5060e9de71e1e19b9460382be","tid":1855832,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"除咗洗手之外<br />\n記住要簽名"},{"pid":"3422f056149a156ff162b71b4ad68477a2464c65","tid":1855832,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b83a5edcca7d98f98957dd2ad651eae283f59630","tid":1855832,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"Done <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df96c9561a05af14a0c3ff3c5cca0654113c3da1","tid":1855832,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"支持狗隊減人工<br />\n全面普選之後你班狗隊就知味道"},{"pid":"7649a086306ff3e086729b8f085142a659a6736a","tid":1855832,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9b355c427c6e441ff8d2a